* To ensure sustainable financing for all levels of TEVET.

Specific macroeconomic objectives for the period of the 7NDP are as follows:
* Achieve an average annual real GDP growth rate of above 5 percent;
* Sustain single-digit inflation;
* Increase  international  reserves to at least 4 months of import cover by;
* Raise domestic revenue collections to over 18 percent of GDP;
* Contain domestic borrowing to less than 2 percent of GDP;
* Reduce the budget deficit to less than 3 percent;
